text: Akbar Mirzoyev (born February 15, 1939)Profile of Akbar Mirzoyev is a Tajikistani politician. He was the Prime Minister of Tajikistan between January 9, 1992, and September 21, 1992. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:Living people Category:Prime ministers of Tajikistan
title: Akbar Mirzoyev
